    "summary": "This is a compact C# .NET command-line project with xUnit tests, first-class runtime logging, agent notes, generated operations docs, and a deterministic verification path.",
    "runtime": ".NET owns restore, formatting, build, runtime execution, and tests. The root namespace is `Generated.CsharpDotnetCli`. Runtime logging is implemented in the starter with quiet text logs on stderr by default and JSON logs controlled by `LOG_LEVEL` and `LOG_FORMAT`. Agent verification goes through `scripts/agent-dotnet` so dotnet home, NuGet package state, and sandbox behavior are predictable.",
    "entrypoints": [
      "src/CsharpDotnetCli/Program.cs",
      "src/CsharpDotnetCli/App.cs",
      "src/CsharpDotnetCli/LoggingConfig.cs",
      "CsharpDotnetCli.slnx"
